{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC07_MAR_710.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f8,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Jeez, no matter how many times you come, a no is still a no!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If you'd show any bit of willingness to compromise, I'd be grateful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Huh? This voice is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I can't let an outsider go inside.<CR>On top of that, you're an amateur<CR>and a woman."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1f9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Sites have rules. Now, go home!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x1fe,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I mean, how many times have I told you this? You don't give up, do ya?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I'd like to say the exact same thing to you, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "...Okay. I'll go home for today,<CR>but I'll come back, no matter how<CR>many times it takes!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x20e,
            "name_id": 0x24,
            "extra_id": 0x204,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Heh, just get outta here!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Goodness...what an obstinate fellow!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "You seem to be having a hard time, Marion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Oh...well, it's the same as always,<CR>so I'm used to it now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "It seems like you've seen all of my disgraceful moments..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "No, that's not true... I don't think...that was disgraceful..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "You're really holding up.<CR>Boss is hardheaded, so when he gets<CR>like that, he won't budge an inch."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I understand that it's part of your job, but maybe you should give up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I won't lose at being hardheaded.<CR>This has become an endurance contest."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x99,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I'll continue to pay him a visit until I'm allowed in!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, that's gonna be hard. Boss doesn't like to let women into the site in the first place..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x9b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "But you're free to enter..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I guess he doesn't treat me as a woman. Hahaha... *sigh*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "But Boss does have a valid point.<CR>It's really dangerous inside the ruin."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I fully understand that, and if I get injured, it's my responsibility."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I see. Then maybe you'll just have to sneak in."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "If you go at night, I'm sure no one'll notice. There's no watch and we keep the entrance open."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "If you want, I can be your guide.<CR>So, whattaya say?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I appreciate your offer, but I'd have to decline."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "My job includes not only investigating, but building good relations with the people of the area."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "When the investigation team comes,<CR>they'll need a trusting relationship<CR>to carry things out smoothly."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I can't enter without permission and lose your boss's trust."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "You have to think about all that to do your job? Being an official must be really hard..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "So you're gonna keep trying until you get official permission? That's hard."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "But, I understand your feelings now. I'll try to talk to Boss for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "I'll tell him to listen more to what you've got to say."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Regina...thank you. Please do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "But, I don't know how much he'll listen to what I tell him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "I'm just having no luck whatsoever."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...this is a difficult problem..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "I understand what your boss is trying to say, but you have your job, too..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "But, I also understand that entering the ruin to do your job is still dangerous..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "But, but, you'll have Linca with you, so I think you might be okay..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, Ayesha, you don't have to look so worried about it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "Thank you, Ayesha. Sorry to make you worry."
        }
    ]
}